Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: The site is located in Newberry County about 3 miles from I-26 access. Newberry is located approximately 45 miles outside of Columbia, the state’s capital, and 60 miles from Greenville, SC.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: 3240 Brittain Drive is a +182,160 SF manufacturing facility in Newberry South Carolina. This +30 acre site has 425 feet of covered rail positions on an active rail spur. The warehouse was originally built in 1966 with an additional +28,000 SF high bay addition in 1971. There is approximately +7,760 SF of office space, 10 dock high doors and 2 on-grade doors.
